Package: k3s-manifest-tool
Version: 1.3-1b
Architecture: all
Maintainer: ChvckN0rri5 <globalfrens@icloud.com>
Depends: bash, dialog, bash-completion
Recommends: sudo
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/ChvckN0rri5/k3s-manifest-tool
Description: CLI tool for managing K3s manifest files
  A CLI tool for managing K3s manifest files, allowing users to move
  files to the K3s manifest directory (retaining original names),
  edit files with nano via a TUI, and refresh an autocompletion cache.
  Requires sudo for secure operations.
Changes: 
  - Corrected manifest.env to add TEXT_EDITOR setting
